    "Make repeated technical versions of the same plugin easier to understand.": "使同一插件的重复技术版本更容易理解。",
    "Make sense of the same plugin appearing as VST, VST3, AU, CLAP, JSFX, or cache variants.": "当同一个插件以 VST、VST3、AU、CLAP、JSFX 或缓存变体出现时，也能整理清楚。",
    "Menu": "菜单",
    "Modern producers own hundreds or thousands of instruments, effects, JSFX, Audio Units, CLAP plugins, and VSTs. Finding the right tool while writing, mixing, or designing sound should feel fast, visual, and personal.": "现在的制作人往往拥有成百上千个乐器、效果器、JSFX、Audio Units、CLAP 和 VST。写歌、混音或设计声音时，找到合适工具应该直观、快速，并且符合自己的习惯。",
    "Move and copy Favorites": "移动和复制收藏",
    "Move through synths, instruments, effects, favorites, and session-building choices without digging through long menus.": "浏览合成器、乐器、效果器、收藏夹和会话构建选项，无需翻阅长菜单。",
    "Move through the browser and update the active plugin preview quickly.": "浏览浏览器并快速更新活动插件预览。",
    "Move, copy, remove, list/unlist, and insert selected Favorites in batches.": "批量移动、复制、删除、列出/取消列出和插入选定的收藏夹。",
    "Multi-column chip filters help narrow large libraries by developer, format family, instrument/effect role, and workflow category.": "多列芯片过滤器有助于按开发人员、格式系列、乐器/效果角色和工作流程类别缩小大型库的范围。",
