    "Search, preview, favorite, thumbnail, note, filter, list or unlist, and insert plugins faster from inside REAPER. Built for producers, mixers, composers, and sound designers who need speed without losing control of their library.": "在 REAPER 内更快搜索、预览、收藏、添加缩略图、记录备注、筛选、显示或隐藏并插入插件。为需要速度也需要掌控感的制作人、混音师、作曲者和声音设计师打造。",
    "Searchable plugin table with listed, unlisted, and all views, status indicators, sorting, keyboard navigation, and multi-selection.": "可搜索的插件表，包含列出的、未列出的和所有视图、状态指示器、排序、键盘导航和多项选择。",
    "Separate VST, VST3, AU, CLAP, JSFX, and REAPER cache variants.": "单独的VST、VST3、AU、CLAP、JSFX 和REAPER 缓存变体。",
    "Session speed": "会话速度",
    "Skip the manual screenshots. The built-in scanner automatically runs in the background to load your plugins onto a temporary track, capture their custom graphical interfaces, and build a beautiful visual grid for you. It automatically ignores unlisted/hidden plugins, skips disconnected external drive paths, and blocklists unstable plugins to prevent DAW crashes.": "无需手动截图。内置的扫描器会自动在后台运行，将您的插件加载到临时轨道上，捕获它们自定义的图形界面，并为您构建美观的视觉网格。它会自动忽略未列出/隐藏的插件，跳过未连接的外接硬盘路径，并将不稳定的插件列入黑名单以防止 DAW 崩溃。",
