    "Use notes, thumbnails, favorites, and category filters to recall the right EQ, compressor, delay, reverb, or utility faster.": "使用音符、缩略图、收藏夹和类别过滤器可以更快地调用正确的均衡器、压缩器、延迟、混响或实用程序。",
